ludwig : requiem for a virgin king ( german : ludwig – requiem für einen jungfräulichen könig ) is a 1972 west german historical drama film directed by hans-jürgen syberberg , starring harry baer as ludwig ii of bavaria . the film was shot on a soundstage with rear-projected scenography and an intentionally artificial style . the film received the deutscher filmpreis for best film and best screenplay . it is the first part in syberberg 's " german trilogy " and was followed by karl may in 1974 and hitler : a film from germany in 1977 .